step.reason:
L(l, m) \in A \\
\text{Consider }(a, b)*(l, m) = (1, 0) = (l, m)*(a, b) \\
\begin{align}
  \implies &(al, b+am)=(1, 0) \\
  \implies &(la, m+lb)=(1, 0) \\
  \implies &la=1, b+am=0 \\
  \implies &l=\dfrac{1}{a},m=-\dfrac{b}{a}
\end{align} \\
\therefore {\bf\text{invertible element} 
  \left(\dfrac{1}{a}, -\dfrac{b}{a}\right)}
